6960, "(fr)After the $r Shivans smashed through our unprepared defences at the $b Phi $b Eridani jump node, all forces in $b Tau $b Sigma have been on full alert. $r Shivan forces, spearheaded by the $h SD $h Azathoth, have entered the system, and although they haven't struck anything larger than a stray freighter yet, we can't take any chances with the lives of civilians."

