7402, "(fr)Our efforts to locate and capture the $h MTD $h Auriga have met with very little success. The vessel has eluded our search teams, though we have forced it into the $b Delphi system, from which we have discovered no stable jump nodes for departure - other than the $b Tegmen node, which is blockaded. We are now commencing a methodical search and scan operation in $b Delphi. The $h Auriga will not escape from our grasp this time."

