7406, "(fr)You will be escorting the $f GTA $f Alacrity in a sweep of $b Delphi spatial sector $b 143-Gamma, near the gas giant $b Delphan. Only an AWACs vessel provides the required sensor clarity over a wide enough area to feasibly cover an entire system, and so half a dozen of the vessels have been deployed. You must ensure the $f Alacrity's safety as it completes a sensor sweep of the area. The vessel has other jobs to complete and didn't come cheap, either."

