7980, "(fr)Destroy the Cthon"

7981, "(fr)Protect the Argentus until its mission is complete"

7982, "(fr)Destroy all other Shivan targets"

7983, "(fr)Defend GTVA vessels"

7984, "(fr)Almost all the civilians and staff are clear. Are you ready, pilots?"

7985, "(fr)As ready as we'll ever be, Control."

7986, "(fr)Very well. Powering up the RBCs now. They're now under our control."

7987, "(fr)This is it. This is the big one, all right."

7988, "(fr)They used to call it going 'over the top', I think. Dates back to 20th Century trench warfare."

7989, "(fr)What happened when you went over the top?"

7990, "(fr)Usually, you died. Life was cheap. Maybe it still is."

7991, "(fr)That's just great. Do you always have to be so negative, Mackie?"

7992, "(fr)Not always... only when we face odds that make winning the Delta Serpentis lottery look easy."

7993, "(fr)We're going to be doing all we can to support you. Play it smart and you won't get killed."

7994, "(fr)At least my hazard pay's gonna be through the roof this month..."

7995, "(fr)One wing of Shivan Dragon fighters has entered the area. These look like Shivan scouts."

7996, "(fr)Play it by the numbers pilots. Interceptors engage, bomber pilots, cover where you can."

7997, "(fr)Roger, Command. We won't let them escape."

7998, "(fr)New contact on scanners, Aten class - it's the GVC Kebechet!"

7999, "(fr)Kebechet, respond at once. Why have you abandoned your post?"

8000, "(fr)The Shivans overran our unit. We are the only survivors. We carry critical information about Shivan movements. Transmitting now."

8001, "(fr)We're pulling the data from the Kebechet's computers now. Stand by."

8002, "(fr)Picking up two new jump signatures! Moloch class!"

8003, "(fr)They have arrived! Fight well for us, our time here has run out."

8004, "(fr)Kebechet is down! Destroy those corvettes pronto, pilots! Don't let them get into Beta Aquilae!"

8005, "(fr)I think that this is what they meant by going over the top..."

8006, "(fr)68 percent of the data was recovered from the Kebechet. Let's hope it's of some use."

8007, "(fr)SCv Ithaqua neutralised! Excellent work pilots, but we're not out of the woods yet."

8008, "(fr)Hastur is going critical! Clear the blast zone!"

8009, "(fr)Both Shivan corvettes have been destroyed."

8010, "(fr)GTC Galahad now on station. Hope we didn't miss the party."

8011, "(fr)Hardly. The Shivan fleet's headed this way. We've taken down two Molochs but there's plenty still to come."

8012, "(fr)I would not call this situation a 'party'."

8013, "(fr)It is a Terran figure of speech, Beta 1."

8014, "(fr)Save the discussion for later, we have another wave of incoming capital ships!"

8015, "(fr)TAG the cruisers. We'll need all the help we can get here."

8016, "(fr)Be careful, pilots! RBC beams do not distinguish friend from foe."

8017, "(fr)There goes the first cruiser."

8018, "(fr)Only one cruiser remains! Destroy that vessel now, pilots!"

8019, "(fr)Great work out there, pilots! All four cruisers have been neutralised."

8020, "(fr)Shivan transports have been destroyed."

8021, "(fr)Primary heat sinks in Cannon 01 have failed. We're going to have to shut her down."

8022, "(fr)Are you kidding? That's one third of our defensive firepower."

8023, "(fr)We can't risk the collateral damage. Mjöllnir 1 powering down..."

8024, "(fr)The GVCv Hetepet has been dispatched to cover the jump node. ETA is three minutes."

8025, "(fr)The SC Abhoth has arrived! She's flanking the cannons!"

8026, "(fr)Mjöllnir 2 is down! Pilots, destroy that vessel before she chews through our whole defence screen!"

8027, "(fr)Main batteries are opening fire now... this should give them something to think about."

8028, "(fr)Excellent work! The SC Abhoth has been eliminated!"

8029, "(fr)Watch Poissons wing! They're attacking your fighters, Alpha!"

8030, "(fr)If you can lure Poissons wing into our field of fire we can help you out with them."

8031, "(fr)Easier said than done! I'm taking fire here!"

8032, "(fr)Look sharp, we have Shivan bombers coming in near the jump node."

8033, "(fr)They've targeted the remaining cannon. The fighters are a diversion!"

8034, "(fr)Mjöllnir 3 has been hit! The jump node defences are down!"

8035, "(fr)Nice to know that Command hasn't forgotten about us here at the most important battle in five years!"

8036, "(fr)Anti-fighter screen initialised. We will assist in clearing the remaining Shivans."

8037, "(fr)Still no sign of the Cthon. Rearm if you have to, she could be here at any moment."

8038, "(fr)That's about as clear a sign as we're going to get, the Cthon has entered the area!"

8039, "(fr)Deploying reserve bombers now. Epsilon wing is at your command."

8040, "(fr)Alpha 1, we're going to be shredded by the Cthon's main cannons if you bombers don't do something about them! "

8041, "(fr)We're on it Hetepet, hang in there."

8042, "(fr)Sustaining critical damage. We won't hold out much longer."

8043, "(fr)Honour our memory with victory, pilots!"

8044, "(fr)This isn't right. Where's the Nyarlathotep? She should've been here by now."

8045, "(fr)Our thoughts exactly, Alpha 2. Rebus Control, did all the Shivans follow the same exit vectors?"

8046, "(fr)Negative - the Nyarlathotep and several smaller vessels left the area on another heading - about twenty minutes ago. Transmitting it to you now."

8047, "(fr)Oh my God, I know where she's going!"

8048, "(fr)Spill it, Mackie."

8049, "(fr)Home. The Nyarlathotep is going home!"

8050, "(fr)Lieutenant Mackie, are you suggesting that she's headed for the Capella jump node?"

8051, "(fr)Why else would the Shivans not stop on their way here? They're not interested in us, we've just been in the way!"

8052, "(fr)This is beginning to make some kind of sense... in that case, what we're fighting here is a diversion."

8053, "(fr)You call THIS a diversion?"

8054, "(fr)That's a rog, Hetepet. Command, request permission to investigate the site of the old Capella node."

8055, "(fr)Denied, Cypher. We need you here to help deal with the Cthon."

8056, "(fr)But Command..."

8057, "(fr)The answer is no. Focus on dealing with the Cthon, we can address this later."

8058, "(fr)Apologies pilots, but there's somewhere we need to be and no time to spare. GTFf Cypher signing off."

8059, "(fr)Captain, this is insubordination! You have your orders!"

8060, "(fr)To hell with orders, you can have my commission if we're wrong about this! Helm, engage subspace drives."

8061, "(fr)Hold your position, Cypher... damn! Pilots, redouble your efforts, the Cthon must be destroyed!"

8062, "(fr)The Cthon's hull integrity is falling! Keep it up, pilots!"

8063, "(fr)Registering a major hull failure on the primary target! We did it! The Cthon is going down!"

8064, "(fr)All right! That one's for the Valhalla, you big son-of-a-bitch!"

8065, "(fr)Shivan bombers have entered the area. Alpha wing, provide assist... hold on, we're receiving a long-range communication signal. Stand by."

8066, "(fr)Command, this is the Cypher. I think you might want to take a look at what's going on over here..."

8067, "(fr)Say again, Cypher? Have you encountered resistance?"

8068, "(fr)There's no time! Scramble the fighters! Scramble EVERYTHING!"

8069, "(fr)Pilots, stand by, it looks like we're going to have to look into this more closely."

8070, "(fr)I knew I was right!"

8071, "(fr)Shut up, Mackie! Let's get back to base, pronto!"

8072, "(fr)The Shivans' guns are damaging our hull. Stop some of their fire or we're done for!"

8073, "(fr)Galahad is down! We have lost the GTC Galahad!"

8074, "(fr)The Cthon has made the jump to subspace! We've lost our chance now, get back to base and let's see if we can limit damage."

8075, "(fr)#Hetepet"

