8120, "(fr)No one's arguing with you now, Mackie. Let's do this. Cypher, Alpha, Beta, Delta and Epsilon wings are moving to give you cover."

8121, "(fr)Thanks, Command, we're managing not too badly. We managed to stay in the Nyarlathotep's blind spot, but her escort are giving us a bit of trouble. We need to get clear soon, and there are incoming bombers."

8122, "(fr)Cypher, this is the Khéphren. Targeting cruisers, get yourself to safety. We will cover you."

8123, "(fr)Affirmative, Khéphren, we're going to need to get things cleared up for the Argentus."

8124, "(fr)At least the Cthon isn't here. We'd be in a lot more trouble than we are now."

8125, "(fr)You don't call this trouble? Kid, if that ship restablizes the node, we'll have a lot more than the Cthon to worry about."

8126, "(fr)We're lucky to have the Khéphren and the Estennu - even then, the odds aren't great."

8127, "(fr)Shut up about the odds and get to work. I don't gamble. We need to clear that path for the Cypher."

8128, "(fr)The Cthulhu is down, the corvette has been eliminated, but there are still several cruisers out there. Keep it sharp people."

8129, "(fr)The Sathla has been destroyed. Keep up the pressure, the Argentus is standing by."

8130, "(fr)The SC Tindalos has been neutralized."

8131, "(fr)That's the rear guard, Alpha. Eliminate what's left of the bombers, and then move to take out the beam cannons."

8132, "(fr)Fight well for us, Alpha. We've done what we can."

8133, "(fr)Damn, we've lost the Estennu."

8134, "(fr)The Khéphren has gone down! Repeat, the Khéphren has gone down!"

8135, "(fr)Dear God, I hope some of them made it to the escape pods."

8136, "(fr)Let's make sure her sacrifice was not in vain. I just hope that she's bought us enough time to do this."

8137, "(fr)We're out of range now, Alpha, get your people in and clear a path for the Argentus."

8138, "(fr)Aye aye, sir. Let's blow this bird, she's pissed me off one too many times."

8139, "(fr)Command, I'm getting a bad feeling about this. We're getting some subspace distortion here... she may be closer to activating the portal than we realized."

8140, "(fr)Are you sure, Cypher?"

8141, "(fr)Very sure, it's now a full blown surge. The gate will be arriving at any moment! Get the Argentus ready, we may have to do this hot! Alpha, get on those beams!"

8142, "(fr)That's it Command, the gate is arriving any second now. Tell the Argentus it's now or never."

8143, "(fr)Affirmative, Cypher. Alpha, do whatever you have to to eliminate those beams immediately!"

8144, "(fr)Whoah... Command, the Knossos has arrived. I'm reading a new corvette and two cruisers. She's starting to stabilize."

8145, "(fr)It's going to be a lot worse if you don't take down those beams, Alpha. The Argentus is on its way, do it NOW!"

8146, "(fr)Argentus is in, Command. This is it, we're making our final run."

8147, "(fr)Godspeed Argentus, we will remember you."

8148, "(fr)Acknowledged. GTCv Argentus, signing off."

8149, "(fr)Alpha, get on those beams! The Argentus won't make impact without your help!"

8150, "(fr)That's one beam cannon down, two to go."

8151, "(fr)Two down! We've almost got it."

8152, "(fr)YEAH! That's it! Command! We did it! The beams are down, repeat the beams are down! Argentus has a free path now!"

8153, "(fr)All remaining pilots, get clear of the blast!"

8154, "(fr)Yeeeeeeehaw! Take that you big ugly bastard! The Nyarlathotep has been destroyed, mission is successful! Repeat, the Nyarlathotep is an expanding cloud! Mission is successful!"

8155, "(fr)My God, what an explosion! "

8156, "(fr)Congratulations, everyone. We barely made that one. You will all receive a commendation for this one."

8157, "(fr)We damn well better, and I will duct tape it to my cockpit."

8158, "(fr)Understood, Mackie, see you back home. Return to base."

8159, "(fr)The Argentus is taking damage, pilot, at this rate, she will not make impact!"

8160, "(fr)The Argentus is losing her hull integrity. Alpha, you're running out of time!"

8161, "(fr)Dear God, no... The Argentus didn't make it... It was our last hope..."

8162, "(fr)What does this mean?"

8163, "(fr)It means unbuckle your belt, lean over and kiss your ass goodbye, kid. The Nyarlathotep is powering up her jump drive. It was nice knowing all of you, but I suspect we're all going to be dead in a few seconds."

8164, "(fr)Oh my God... Oh my God... We're done for..."

8165, "(fr)See you in Hell, kid."

